      <title>普京押注特朗普将提供他想要的乌克兰优惠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/putin-bets-trump-delivers-on-ukraine-while-priming-for-more-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据莫斯科熟悉此事的人们说，俄罗斯仍在指望美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在乌克兰达成可接受的和平协议，尽管它准备继续战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/putin-bets-trump-delivers-on-ukraine-while-priming-for-more-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 11:19:44 GMT</pubDate>
